ca.openosp.openo.commn.model.inbox.InboxQueryParameters
ca.openosp.openo.commn.model.inbox.OscarInboxQueryParameters
public class OscarInboxQueryParameters extends InboxQueryParameters
An abstract class to collect and pass inbox query parameters Extending classes should translate provided parameters to the valid formats used by the inbox repository
